CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 9, 1963, pg. 4, reads: "Dazzling D.I.s were presented to the guests Sunday night at their MENDS benefit show and dance at Holiday House. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of unknown woman, and Margaret Watson wearing light colored sleeveless dress with tie and bow at waist, light colored shoes, and gloves, standing in Holiday House for D. I. Club's annual MENDS benefit
